Project Scope
  1 Task Management
    1.1 Add a new task with title and description
    1.2 Edit an existing task
    1.3 Delete a task
    1.4 Mark task as completed
    1.5 Set task priority (Low, Medium, High)
    1.6 Set due date for a task
  2 Task Organization
    2.1 View all tasks
    2.2 View completed tasks
    2.3 View pending tasks
    2.4 Sort tasks by due date
    2.5 Sort tasks by priority
    2.6 Search tasks by keyword
  3 Categories
    3.1 Create task categories (School, Work, Personal, etc.)
    3.2 Assign tasks to categories
    3.3 Edit category name
    3.4 Delete category
  4 Data Storage
    4.1 Save tasks locally
    4.2 Load saved tasks when application starts
  5 Other
    5.1 Simple and user-friendly interface
    5.2 Color marking based on priority
    5.3 Scroll support when necessary
